      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the FDA guidance for ASTM F1717 submissions for pedicle screw systems. These QoIs directly inform fatigue life prediction and structural adequacy under physiological loading envelopes."
    },
