      "rationale": "Validation performed on the exact production design under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending, which is the COU. Two independent laboratories provide cross-site reproducibility evidence. The FEA ensemble spanning three institutions further demonstrates model robustness. Validation activities are directly mapped to COU requirements with no extrapolation required."
